8-1704.CFTC rule, defined.

CFTC rule shall mean any rule, regulation, or order of the Commodity Futures Trading Commission in effect on January 1, 2025.

SourceLaws 1987, LB 575, § 4;Laws 1993, LB 283, § 2;Laws 2011, LB76, § 4;Laws 2019, LB259, § 6;Laws 2020, LB909, § 16;Laws 2021, LB363, § 15;Laws 2022, LB707, § 23;Laws 2023, LB92, § 15;Laws 2024, LB1074, § 49;Laws 2025, LB251, § 16.Effective Date: March 12, 2025
